1)  If you 'talk' to Gorrtoth, the Beast Lord, he will mention a book called
    the Necronoicon. Ask him about that and he will refer to the Staff of Ages.
    Ask him about that and he will mention Galbert, and old man.
2)  Find Galbert in a hut in Drakmere. Ask him about the "staff of ages" and
    he will mention items that may help you. Ask him about "items" and he will
    provide a few figures.
3)  Use this figures to make your way through a maze and press the skull on
    the wall. This formerly provided a Staff of Ages as a reward.

2500 XP
